(249, 2, '2013-11-11 16:42:45', '2013-11-11 16:42:45', '<div>Received this from one of our patients!</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small;">If you have Cox DVR services, go to  "Freezone" , then tab to "Health and Wellness",  then tab to "Mag Rack  Fitness"  and you will get a wonderful selection of </span><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small;">exercise videos that are exactly 30 minutes.   They have everything from areobics to yoga. Even Bollywood dance (LOL).    So, if somebody tells you they can''t afford a gym membership or  exensive CD''s, if they have DVR services, that''s all they need. </span></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small;">Mag Rack changes every 3 months so you don''t get stuck in the same  routines. Some are easy to get you started, some more advanced and even some for  people over 50. </span>This way I just turn on the TV and there it is, any time of the day or  night. No excuses about why I can''t fit in a workout.</div>', 'Free exercise videos', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'free-exercise-videos', '', '', '2013-11-25 16:09:24', '2013-11-25 16:09:24', '', 0, 'http://www.drjchen.com/blog/?p=249', 0, 'post', '', 0),
