(180, 2, '2013-10-09 16:10:24', '2013-10-09 16:10:24', 'Welcome!! This is a new section for everyone to share their positive experiences, tips, recipes and encouragement for others doing this program as well! It is completely anonymous and if you would like to make a comment, the user ID and password is posted at the end of my blog on the right-hand side of the page if you hover over the title. Once you are logged in, click on "Heart Health" under "Forum" and there will be a box to leave your comments in. Click submit and it will be posted.\n\nI will be making announcements and posting encouragements here also. <strong><em>Please use this as a way to support each other in your goal to a healthy lifestyle!</em> </strong>\n\n-Dr. Patience McCoy', 'Share here!', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '172-autosave-v1', '', '', '2013-10-09 16:10:24', '2013-10-09 16:10:24', '', 172, 'http://www.drjchen.com/blog/?p=180', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
