(288, 2, '2013-11-25 16:38:59', '2013-11-25 16:38:59', '****Results for Mr. B. after 3 months:  Lost 11lbs, BP down from 148/84 to 120/62, Triglycerides significantly improved from 256 to 132, Glucose levels from 160 to 107.\r\n\r\nMr. B. has had trouble managing his diabetes with prescription medication for 20 years but within 3 shorts months of following the website, he is finally able to cut down on his diabetes medication.  His inspiring success story involves eating more vegetables and fruit, eliminating white bread, white rice, and white potatoes, appropriate portion sizes of protein with each meal, and a regular exercise routine.  Mr. B. admits it was a little difficult in the beginning to change his eating habits but he was armed with will power.  Now that he can feel and see a tremendous change, he will never go back! Congratulations!!\r\n\r\n***Results for Mr. H. after 3 months: Lost 15 lbs.  BP down 144/83 to 102/64. Cholesterol significantly improved: Total cholesterol 283 down to 195; Triglycerides 356 down to 128; LDL 178 down to 128. EXCELLENT!!\r\n\r\n***I just wanted to drop a line and tell you how much I am enjoying this website. The charts and graphs tracking my development have been very helpful to me. I find that you can really see the difference between your weight and your blood pressure on days when you would adhere to the program. It''s amazing how diet and exercise have to work together to get you the results you want!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'NEW Encouraging Patient Results', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '120-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-11-25 16:38:59', '2013-11-25 16:38:59', '', 120, 'http://www.drjchen.com/blog/?p=288', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
