(1417, 6, '2022-06-08 17:19:10', '2022-06-08 17:19:10', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Best Friend Fridays&#x2122; celebrate our pet companions who are always there for us – helping us handle stress and boosting our physical and mental health. Having a pet is a Healthy Bond for Life&#x2122; that may help you live a longer, healthier life! (And we’ve got the science to prove it.)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Pets can help you:</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>deal with stress</li><li>get more exercise and meet fitness goals</li><li>feel less lonely and isolated</li><li>lose weight</li><li>lower blood pressure and cholesterol levels</li><li>recover after a health event</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Owning a dog can help prevent chronic conditions such as diabetes and depression, and simply petting a dog helps lower blood pressure.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->\n<h3>Pets get us through hard times.</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->\n<h3>During the pandemic, according to a Rover survey:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>53% of U.S. adults got a new dog, 32% got a new cat and 14% got both.</li><li>93% said their “pandemic pet” improved their mental and/or physical well-being.</li><li>80% said it made working from home more enjoyable, and they were able to bond with their pet more during this time.</li><li>Pets make work better.</li><li>40% of pet owners feel anxious about leaving pets at home if they go back to work in person.</li><li>44% would consider changing jobs for a pet-friendly workplace and 37% would give up vacation time and take a pay cut to bring their pet to work.</li><li>Having a pet around while working can help reduce stress, increase productivity and improve employee satisfaction, teamwork and collaboration.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At work or at play, pets are the best. Take time each Friday to celebrate your pets and all they add to your life and post a photo or video using #BestFriendFridays.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Learn more about Healthy Bond for Life’s Best Friend Fridays at heart.org/pets.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Less stress. Lots of love.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'less-stress-lots-of-love', '', '', '2022-06-22 18:41:46', '2022-06-22 18:41:46', '', 0, 'http://www.drjchen.com/blog/?p=1417', 0, 'post', '', 0),
